cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper discusses a regularization technique for Recurrent Neural Networks (RNNs) with Long Short-Term Memory (LSTM) units. This makes it likely to belong to the following sub-categories: 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning)
- cs.CL (Computation and Language)
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition)
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence)
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing)
